{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said she was a young girl of about 16.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would have parties in their backyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they even have photos that they took from their backyard, looking right into-- right across the electric wire fence, through which everything was quite visible.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could see our barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could see the electric wire fence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could see the factory and the logo, Continental.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and she said, at night, we would hear these terrible screams.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What were they, indeed?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, I explained to her that-- that-- what happened, that the civilians didn't like to see us get beaten on the job.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of-- some of us just went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were so exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people just collapsed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and civilians reacted to the beating of someone so helpless.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at night, they would be called out, and they would-- they would get the punishment in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, the-- they screamed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And across the street, where she lived, she would overhear these screams, and 47 years later, relate it to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- Why do you think they didn't do anything about it when they heard the screams?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was nothing she could do about it, she said, because her father, who was a Communist was-- was a Communist and they printed a newspaper, an underground newspaper and-- in this little place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her mother had everybody's little Communist book, members book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry, not members of the Communist Party, but the-- the people who subscribed to this little newspaper.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when-- when the Gestapo came in from the street, they had to come down a couple of steps into the yard and walk a bit to the house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her mother noticed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
